reporting_requirements.sanctions:
A fine of up to EUR 800.000 for violation of the reporting obligation for legal persons or associations of persons with an average annual turnover of more than EUR 400 million;

For example, a fine of up to EUR 100.000 may be imposed on anyone who willfully or negligently fails to keep documentation or fails to keep it for at least seven years contrary to the provisions of the LkSG; fails to prepare a report correctly; fails to make a report referred to therein publicly available or fails to do so in good time; fails to submit a report or fails to do so in good time.

