regulatory_requirements.key_actions:
Efficient risk management system;
Regular and systematic assessment of the risks of human rights and environmental violations in the supply chain;
Development and implementation of measures to avoid identified risks;
Introduction of internal and external grievance mechanisms that enable affected persons to report grievances;
Ensuring that suppliers and business partners also comply with human rights and environmental standards;
Training for employees and suppliers on the requirements of the LkSG and on human rights and environmental due diligence obligations;
Co-operate with NGOs, trade unions and other relevant stakeholders to better identify risks and develop effective measures.

scope:
